{"tid":415081,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"無宗教信仰嘅你，認為人死咗之後會點？","createTime":"2017-09-26T16:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T09:14:26.000Z","uid":54720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5deba1b67957d218ed8aefd84bda269f6ca4b3","tid":415081,"uid":54720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"我認為意識會依然存在，<br />\n雖然塵世嘅物質帶唔走，<br />\n但記憶同知識會帶得走。<br />\n<br />\n有時候會諗，人老咗，記憶衰退，懵下懵下先死，會成為一隻糊塗嘅靈體。<br />\n反而，年輕不幸過世嘅，可以繼續以年輕嘅思維同埋靈體嘅狀態去暢遊呢世界。"},{"pid":"66a8b3b89b687a21677152cd5b0e648d2655cfb3","tid":415081,"uid":142466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"無諗得太複雜，覺得死咗好似瞓着咗咁，世界發生咩事都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e58fcc60b37de64c2e168970daf20387ae17256","tid":415081,"uid":43406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"生同死並無分別<br />\n只係一個空間去另一個空間<br />\n只係一種過程<br />\n並唔需要賦予特別嘅意義係生死之間<br />\n睇唔到死後嘅景況只係你未到果個階段"},{"pid":"9610b45f2798095b46cdab59d9f191426c46a9e5","tid":415081,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"人死後去另一個次元"},{"pid":"0f45919c50db7b18301143a6a5136aa9fecebc41","tid":415081,"uid":107157,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:58:10.000Z","msg":"你既思考=腦電波(神經元神經脈衝)<br />\n死左=冇電=冇思考=屍體一舊(回歸自然做養分)<br />\n<br />\n好聽啲咁講 你既存在係由其他生物既死去而產生，而你死去就會化作呢個世界既一部分，不斷循環。簡單啲黎講，你就係我，我就係你，一即係全，全即係一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108b94b7b3192de24742ea02c735d270f7de4bda","tid":415081,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:59:15.000Z","msg":"Btw樓主開係創意台想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人死後會有個叫上帝既人帶你上天堂日日屌女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e4724f7543ee869b81d536fac18817672bae26","tid":415081,"uid":54720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a835f5f45169d0df33c64cfd2ccb6d034b9b3d4","tid":415081,"uid":87497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:01:36.000Z","msg":"覺得人死左，就好似平時訓覺又冇發夢果種感覺。"},{"pid":"18d4140f492491d0a621af23c7b419dfb939de03","tid":415081,"uid":55826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無諗得太複雜，覺得死咗好似瞓着咗咁，世界發生咩事都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神作"},{"pid":"1f83d7791f9cbfd7760aace39917aa9c28f15ea8","tid":415081,"uid":132446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我認為意識會依然存在，<br />\n雖然塵世嘅物質帶唔走，<br />\n但記憶同知識會帶得走。<br />\n<br />\n有時候會諗，人老咗，記憶衰退，懵下懵下先死，會成為一隻糊塗嘅靈體。<br />\n反而，年輕不幸過世嘅，可以繼續以年輕嘅思維同埋靈體嘅狀態去暢遊呢世界。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來我係電腦世界其中一個NPC, 格式化咩都無<br />\n完"},{"pid":"8a6e2367ef07ec8cf9f072117d7462cb1a469553","tid":415081,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比啲意見好啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368f38aa3a55c8fd605022ff94ccccb5054a8a22","tid":415081,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:18:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"da89c98c753306b4ab801d2846d6b1c4d5234a44","tid":415081,"uid":35557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"黑"},{"pid":"0c49fe95dfa25a48decd67c76cff0c73a5f2e951","tid":415081,"uid":31733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得死左之後，<br />\n靈魂會係死既位置一直存在，<br />\n直至存在開始被磨滅"},{"pid":"28c220c23458a47b7e62775ffa83a3e95757c2ed","tid":415081,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"乜都無，同你出世前一樣"},{"pid":"3cdde68cc6c6b9114e51df582d2f8997d3a77854","tid":415081,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"人死如燈滅"},{"pid":"cc2130851d282ccf30fcdf5dddddc0faeb809295","tid":415081,"uid":54720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你既思考=腦電波(神經元神經脈衝)<br />\n死左=冇電=冇思考=屍體一舊(回歸自然做養分)<br />\n<br />\n好聽啲咁講 你既存在係由其他生物既死去而產生，而你死去就會化作呢個世界既一部分，不斷循環。簡單啲黎講，你就係我，我就係你，一即係全，全即係一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得死後嘅境況唔應該用純科學角度去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7dce289e57b7ed6d56fb5c60dc40bdfbb3dbd9","tid":415081,"uid":54720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜都無，同你出世前一樣</blockquote><br />\n可能只係你唔記得，你都唔記得你一歲時候嘅事，但你當時係有意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}